#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:24
msgid "Sponge"
msgstr "Belakia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:25
msgid "Removes water on contact"
msgstr "Ura kentzen du kontaktatzean"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:26
msgid ""
"Sponges are blocks which remove water around them when they are placed or "
"come in contact with water, turning it into a wet sponge."
msgstr ""
"Belakiak blokeak dira, inguruan duten ura edo kontaktuan dagoena kentzen "
"dutenak, belaki busti bihurtuz."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:117
msgid "Waterlogged Sponge"
msgstr "Bustitako Belaki"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:118 mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:133
msgid "Can be dried in furnace"
msgstr "Labe batean lehortu daiteke"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:119
msgid ""
"A waterlogged sponge can be dried in the furnace to turn it into (dry) "
"sponge. When there's an empty bucket in the fuel slot of a furnace, the "
"water will pour into the bucket."
msgstr ""
"Urez bustitako belaki bat labean lehortu daiteke, belaki lehor bihurtzeko. "
"Labe bateko erregai-artekan ontzi huts bat dagoenean, ura ontzira isurtzen "
"da."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:132
msgid "Riverwaterlogged Sponge"
msgstr "Ibai-urarekin Bustitako Belakia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:134
msgid ""
"This is a sponge soaking wet with river water. It can be dried in the "
"furnace to turn it into (dry) sponge. When there's an empty bucket in the "
"fuel slot of the furnace, the river water will pour into the bucket."
msgstr ""
"Hau ibaiko urarekin belaki busti bat da. Labean lehortu daiteke belaki "
"(lehor) bihurtzeko. Labeko erregai-artekan balde huts bat dagoenean, ibaiko "
"ura baldean isurtzen da."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_sponges/init.lua:134
msgid ""
"A sponge becomes riverwaterlogged (instead of waterlogged) if it sucks up "
"more river water than (normal) water."
msgstr ""
"Belaki bat ibai-urez bustitakoa bihurtzen da (ur arruntarekin beharrean), ur "
"(arrunta) baino ibai-ur gehiago xurgatzen badu."
